      "title": "The Mad Magician (1954)",
      "description": "The Mad Magician is a 1954 American horror film directed by John Brahm starring Vincent Price, Mary Murphy and Eva Gabor. It follows Don Gallico, a master illusionist who, after being betrayed by his employer and losing his wife to him, seeks revenge by murdering the man who wronged him. Disguised as a rival magician, he continues to perform while trying to cover up his crimes, leading to a series of dark and thrilling events.",
